OL,7,FThe school, founded and led by
OL,8,Fheadteacher Katharine Birbalsingh, a
OL,9,Fformer government social mobility
OL,10,Ftsar, argued its prayer policy was
OL,11,Fjustified after it faced death and
OL,12,Fbomb threats linked to religious
OL,13,Fobservance on site.
OL,15,FIn a written ruling on Tuesday, Mr
OL,16,FJustice Linden dismissed the pupil's
OL,17,Farguments against the prayer rituals
OL,18,Fban.
