OL,7,FThe judge upheld the student's
OL,8,Fchallenge to a decision to temporarily
OL,9,Fexclude her from the school.
OL,11,FLawyers for the pupil told the judge
OL,12,Fat a hearing in January that she was
OL,13,Fmaking a "modest" request to be
OL,14,Fallowed to pray for around five
OL,15,Fminutes at lunch time, on dates when
OL,16,Ffaith rules required it, but not
OL,17,Fduring lessons.
