OL,7,FShe added: "My daughter's impassioned
OL,8,Fstance compelled me to support her and
OL,9,FI stand firm in that decision.
OL,11,F"Her courage in pursuing this matter
OL,12,Ffills me with pride and I'm confident
OL,13,Fshe's gained invaluable lessons from
OL,14,Fthe experience."
OL,16,FImam Ajmal Masroor told ITV News he is
OL,17,F"disappointed" with the decision made
OL,18,Fby the High Court and claimed it
OL,19,F"excludes" Muslim children from daily
OL,20,Fpractice.
