OL,7,F"It's a very basic human right to
OL,8,Fpray, what's wrong with prayers," he
OL,9,Fquestioned.
OL,11,F"This a terrible day, this is a
OL,12,Fterrible tragedy for integration, it's
OL,13,Fa day when we are legally saying to
OL,14,Four kids, 'it's okay to other you,
OL,15,Fit's okay to push you outside and it's
OL,16,Fokay to exclude you because you're a
OL,17,FMuslim'."
OL,19,FImam Ajmal Masroor spoke to ITV News
OL,20,Fin the wake of the decision,
OL,21,Fdescribing it as a "terrible day"
